    "summary": "A high-trust, accessible mobile banking design system prioritizing data legibility, secure biometric workflows, and clear financial visualization.",
    "description": "The visual philosophy is built on 'Institutional Trust' and 'Radical Clarity'. We utilize a deep navy primary palette (#1E3A8A) to evoke stability, contrasted with vibrant functional colors for actions. The UI prioritizes data legibility through the use of tabular figures and high-contrast typography. The system is strictly componentized to support React Native's cross-platform rendering, ensuring a native feel on both iOS and Android while maintaining brand consistency.",
