    "layout_strategy": "Mobile-first flexbox layout using React Native's StyleSheet API. The layout relies on a vertical stack for the main content area with safe-area insets respected. On larger screens (tablets), the layout shifts to a two-column grid with navigation on the left rail.",
    "visual_philosophy": "Trust through consistency. We avoid decorative clutter, focusing on the data. The color palette is restrained, using color only to indicate interactivity or status (Green for credit, Red for debit/error). Motion is used sparingly to guide the user through state changes.",
    "information_architecture": "The app uses a flat hierarchy with a persistent bottom navigation bar giving access to core domains: Home (Dashboard), Move Money (Transfers), Savings, and Profile. Critical flows like Transfers are presented as modal stacks to maintain context.",
    "responsive_strategy": "The app utilizes a fluid layout system. Components use percentage-based widths or flex-grow properties. Typography scales using the device's font scale settings. Breakpoints are used primarily to adjust padding and grid columns on tablet devices.",
    "ui_patterns": [
      "Bottom Navigation for primary views",
      "Modal Sheets for complex actions (Transfers)",
      "Biometric Interstitials for sensitive ops",
      "Skeleton Loading states for financial data",
      "Toast Notifications for transaction status"
    ],
